'BRUN PRINT SCRN CAT' WILL INSTALLTHE FOLLOWING COMMANDS TO APPLESOFT:<CTRL>-E ERASES THE 40-COLUMN SCREEN<CTRL>-C CATALOGS A DOS 3.3 DISK<CTRL>-P ACTIVATES A PRINTER IN SLOT1 AND AWAITS A COMMAND LETTER: 'S'PRINTS THE 40-COLUMN SCREEN. 'C' PRINTS THE DOS 3.3 CATALOGWITHOUT PAUSING; 'Q' EXITS PRINTERMODE.<CTRL>-Q QUITS; DISCONNECTING THEUTILITY.